when it got infested with bugs.

62
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:24,350
In just a few years,
it was completely eaten away.

63
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:31,830
Termites.

64
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,920
It's termites.

65
00:04:33,390 --> 00:04:35,320
The trees in our village
are most afraid of such things.

66
00:04:37,390 --> 00:04:38,110
Do you think this is it?

67
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:47,480
What do you want to do?

68
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:49,350
Imagine

69
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:53,070
countless termites crawling on you

70
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:54,510
and biting you slowly.

71
00:04:54,670 --> 00:04:55,720
Where they pass,

72
00:04:55,830 --> 00:04:58,670
they leave behind tiny holes,

73
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:01,790
and these holes connect to form furrows.

74
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:02,760
In the end,

75
