Never mind.

104
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:16,040
If you don't want to come with us,

105
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:17,390
I won't force you.

106
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,670
I just feel sorry for you.

107
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:22,790
Finally, there is a place
with no discrimination

108
00:06:22,830 --> 00:06:23,550
and no bullying,

109
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:26,040
and people there admire medical skills,

110
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:29,720
but you just let it pass by.

111
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,830
Well, later,

112
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:35,920
