Yes.

125
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:07,110
If you have any more problems,
just come to us.

126
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,720
Don't go to the Tianyin Palace.

127
00:07:09,070 --> 00:07:10,160
Yes.

128
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:13,920
It's our fault for not knowing
how powerful you are.

129
00:07:14,070 --> 00:07:15,760
