168
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:49,200
All right.

169
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,110
I'll take it.

170
00:08:51,110 --> 00:08:51,910
That's it.

171
00:08:51,910 --> 00:08:53,110
Put it away.

172
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,760
You're free now. You can leave.

173
00:09:03,550 --> 00:09:05,760
Well, are you envious?

174
00:09:07,110 --> 00:09:08,350
