202
00:10:40,670 --> 00:10:41,960
I'll tell you the truth.

203
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:45,030
You're a fairly rare
mutant spiritual root.

204
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:47,550
As long as you follow me
and cultivate yourself diligently,

205
00:10:48,350 --> 00:10:50,550
defeating Mu Bai Zhenren
won't be a problem.

206
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:56,910
Who is Mu Bai Zhenren?

207
00:10:58,400 --> 00:10:59,000
Mu Bai?

208
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:05,520
He's a young genius
in the cultivation world.

209
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:07,280
Isn't it great
that we just live peacefully together,

210
00:11:07,350 --> 00:11:09,030
built foundation and have fun?

211
00:11:09,350 --> 00:11:10,910
But we heard that this guy

212
00:11:11,150 --> 00:11:12,230
formed his core at five,

213
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:13,350
established his foundation at eight,

214
00:11:13,350 --> 00:11:15,790
and had his Nascent Soul
take form at eighteen.

215
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,080
As a result,

216
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,640
the disciples who diligently cultivated

217
00:11:19,760 --> 00:11:21,520
had to be nagged
by our master every day.

218
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:26,470
I'm incompetent. I'll be grateful
for your patience, Master.

219
00:11:30,550 --> 00:11:31,470
Do you agree?

220
00:11:37,590 --> 00:11:39,710
Good. From today on,

221
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:42,640
you'll be my first disciple.

222
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:44,910
You have to make me proud.

223
00:11:45,670 --> 00:11:47,470
Your lifelong mission is to defeat
your senior master,

224
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:49,440
Mu Bai Zhenren.

225
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:50,710
Do you remember?

226
00:11:51,790 --> 00:11:53,110
[Qingyuan Sect]
Master!

227
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:56,960
I'm finally back.

228
00:11:58,670 --> 00:11:59,600
Master!

229
00:12:00,230 --> 00:12:01,080
You know what,

230
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,520
I caught
a thousand-year-old locust tree spirit.

231
00:12:02,550 --> 00:12:04,360
I even received a banner. Look.

232
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:05,600
My disciple.

233
00:12:07,520 --> 00:12:08,400
You're back.

234
00:12:10,520 --> 00:12:11,870
I've been missing you.

235
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:12,960
Master.

236
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,750
I've suffered so much.

237
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:15,670
My goodness.

238
00:12:15,670 --> 00:12:16,750
Bai.

239
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,870
You're finally back.

240
00:12:20,280 --> 00:12:21,040
Oh, my God.

241
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:24,160
The Qingyuan Sect is saved!

242
00:12:26,790 --> 00:12:27,430
Hello.

243
00:12:27,630 --> 00:12:29,960
Master, I've only been gone for one day,

244
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,720
and your eyesight has worsened so much.

245
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:33,280
Your favorite disciple is here.

246
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,040
Bai.

247
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:36,040
Where have you been
for the past 100 years?

248
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:37,520
Bai?

249
00:12:38,990 --> 00:12:39,310
What?

250
00:12:39,310 --> 00:12:42,040
He's my new disciple, Cui Chen.

251
00:12:42,230 --> 00:12:43,520
He's not Bai.

252
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:45,670
My name is Cui Chen,

253
00:12:45,990 --> 00:12:48,990
but my Daoist title
in the Core Formation Phase is Mu Bai.

254
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:56,110
How did my disciple

255
00:12:56,190 --> 00:12:58,400
become Mu Bai?

256
00:12:58,960 --> 00:13:00,670
He's been missing for over 100 years.

257
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,430
Why did I run into him?

258
00:13:03,230 --> 00:13:05,040
People are treacherous.

259
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:06,750
Liar.

260
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:08,520
A big liar!

261
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:11,550
You're my best disciple indeed.

262
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:12,310
Of course.

263
00:13:13,110 --> 00:13:14,310
Master.

264
00:13:14,430 --> 00:13:16,750
