275
00:13:33,870 --> 00:13:34,550
I...

276
00:13:35,520 --> 00:13:37,110
How could I have known

277
00:13:37,110 --> 00:13:38,160
my unrelated disciple

278
00:13:38,160 --> 00:13:39,600
would be the despicable Mu Bai?

279
00:13:39,870 --> 00:13:41,670
Don't call him that. He is your senior.

280
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:43,160
You should call him Senior.

281
00:13:44,110 --> 00:13:44,990
